sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Buyer/Client
    participant S as Merchant/Server
    participant F as Facilitator
    participant B as Mezo Blockchain

    C->>S: GET /paid
    S-->>C: 402 PAYMENT-REQUIRED<br/>{ scheme: exact, network: eip155:31611,<br/>  price: "$0.01" mUSD, payTo }
    C-->>C: Sign EIP-712 message<br/>as payment payload
    C->>S: retry GET /paid<br/>with PAYMENT-SIGNATURE
    S->>F: POST /verify<br/>PAYMENT-SIGNATURE + PAYMENT-REQUIRED
    F-->>S: 200 Verification
    S-->>S: Do work
    S->>F: POST /settle<br/>PAYMENT-SIGNATURE + PAYMENT-REQUIRED
    F->>B: Submit mUSD transfer tx
    B-->>F: tx confirmed
    F-->>S: 200 Settled, tx_hash
    S-->>C: 200 OK<br/>PAYMENT-RESPONSE + Content
